title: Trump swearing video: Says Iran, Israel ‘don’t know what the f—’ they’re doing
description:
President Donald Trump swore Tuesday morning while talking to reporters about the faltering ceasefire between Israel and Iran. Trump was speaking with reporters at the White House before departing for the NATO summit. He expressed disappointment about the continued attacks.
